sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Predictor Controller
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Runtime<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Puller as Storage Helper<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Runtime as Model Server Runtime<br/>varies gRPC/HTTP
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant Service as Kubernetes Service

    Note over User,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Registration and Loading
    User->>K8sAPI: POST Predictor CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>etcd: Store metadata<br/>HTTP (no encryption)
    Controller->>ModelMesh: Register model<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Load model request<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP
    Adapter->>Puller: Pull model artifacts<br/>gRPC 8086/TCP
    Puller->>S3: Download model<br/>HTTPS (Access Key/IAM)
    S3-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    Puller-->>Adapter: Model ready
    Adapter->>Runtime: Load model<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Model loaded
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Load complete
    ModelMesh-->>Controller: Model ready
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Predictor status

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: Inference Request (gRPC)
    Client->>Service: gRPC inference request<br/>8033/TCP (application-level auth)
    Service->>ModelMesh: Route to pod<br/>8033/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Forward request<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    Adapter->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>gRPC
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Prediction result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>Service: Result
    Service-->>Client: Prediction response

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: Inference Request (REST)
    Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    Service->>RESTProxy: HTTP request<br/>8008/TCP
    RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Forward request<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    Adapter->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>gRPC
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Prediction result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>Service: HTTP JSON response
    Service-->>Client: Prediction result

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: ServingRuntime Provisioning
    User->>K8sAPI: POST ServingRuntime CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate resource<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification
    Controller->>etcd: Store runtime config<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Deployment created
